, "w": 1}, {"a": "brent", "b": "hormuz", "w": 1}, {"a": "commodities", "b": "oil", "w": 1}, {"a": "crudeoil", "b": "oil", "w": 1}]}, "top_tweets": [{"id": "2073954098877972592", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2073954098877972592", "text": "This isn't normal. \n\nIt's like draining your savings account to zero and calling yourself richer. \n\nIt's OK not to understand oil markets. \n\nIt's not OK to pretend you do, @DavidInglesTV \n\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket", "time": "02:16", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 19826, "likes": 258, "replies": 14, "retweets": 20, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 18, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2073994748151611661", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2073994748151611661", "text": "ADNOC today launched a global LNG\nmarketing and trading platform in Abu Dhabi Global Market (ADGM), combining the marketing activities of ADNOC Gas and XRG with the trading capabilities of ADNOC Trading into an\nintegrated commercial platform. #OOTT #Adnoc", "time": "04:57", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 17303, "likes": 65, "replies": 6, "retweets": 22, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Natural gas"]}}, {"id": "2074004028699414748", "url": "https://x.com/LukeyTrags/status/2074004028699414748", "text": "The world is transitioning to hydrocarbons @realhagetaka #OOTT #COM $OIL $COAL", "time": "05:34", "author": "LukeyTrags", "author_name": "Hydrocarbon", "followers": 5697, "views": 2380, "likes": 19, "replies": 1, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": ["Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2074010754609455468", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074010754609455468", "text": "“… officials in Abu Dhabi needed enough ships to make the risky transit — not just once, but over and over. \n\nAnd for that they turned for help to Ga-Hyun Chung, the intensely private Korean shipping tycoon…”\n\nhttps://t.co/uCaWia5WvQ", "time": "06:01", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 75369, "likes": 171, "replies": 10, "retweets": 33, "quotes": 6, "bookmarks": 41, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "UAE"]}}, {"id": "2074037761254809627", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074037761254809627", "text": "A flotilla of Japanese oil tankers and other vessels is leaving at once the Strait of Hormuz via the Iranian shipping lane. \n\nThe group includes six VLCCs carrying ~12 million barrels from Saudi Arabia and the United Arab Emirates that were trapped for ~100 days.", "time": "07:48", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 98613, "likes": 555, "replies": 20, "retweets": 104, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 38, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}, {"id": "2074066953870909948", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2074066953870909948", "text": "PSA: China is starting to buy again.\n\n#oott", "time": "09:44", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 42465, "likes": 188, "replies": 6, "retweets": 32, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 34, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["China demand", "Demand outlook"]}}, {"id": "2074105592885461149", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074105592885461149", "text": "Saudi Aramco cuts the official selling price (OSP) for Arab light for Asia by USD 11.00/bbl to USD -1.50/bbl versus the benchmark (Oman/Dubai average) for the month of August  #oott", "time": "12:18", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 6077, "likes": 34, "replies": 1, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074106261759549504", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074106261759549504", "text": "Saudi Arabia slashes the official selling price of its flagship Arab Light, pricing the barrels for Asia delivery at **minus** $1.5 a barrel to the Dubai benchmark.\n\nIt's the largest **discount** for Arab Light to Asia since mid-2020, when the world was still battling Covid-19.", "time": "12:20", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 220955, "likes": 626, "replies": 41, "retweets": 109, "quotes": 26, "bookmarks": 60, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074109664988483924", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074109664988483924", "text": "CHART OF THE DAY: Saudi Arabia has only offered its flagship Arab Light for Far East delivery at minus $1.5 a barrel (or cheaper) twice in the last 25 years: once during the 2015 price war against US shale, and again in 2020 during the price war against Russia. That's it. https://t.co/LvTeYoPSBP", "time": "12:34", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 198207, "likes": 527, "replies": 26, "retweets": 147, "quotes": 23, "bookmarks": 103, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2074170124718817317", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2074170124718817317", "text": "US SPR crude inventories fell by ~6.2mb w/w to a multi year low of 319.5mb last week #oott        \n\nSour down ~2.7mb to 202.8mb    \nSweet down ~3.4mb to 116.7mb https://t.co/c8ihfX5SNU", "time": "16:34", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 71349, "likes": 185, "replies": 8, "retweets": 37, "quotes": 13, "bookmarks": 25, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories"]}}, {"id": "2074172334697578614", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074172334697578614", "text": "Dear Arabica coffee contract, \n\nplease, stop right now what you are doing.\n\nYours truly, \n\nsomeone who needs caffeine to deal with oil", "time": "16:43", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 51578, "likes": 342, "replies": 22, "retweets": 16, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Positive", "topics": []}}, {"id": "2074175742565380153", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2074175742565380153", "text": "Cuba suffers another nation-wide power blackout (the 2nd this year to affect the whole of the island). \n\nCuba has been suffering from rolling blackouts since mid 2025, at times affecting as much as 75% of the population. But complete, nationwide grid collapses had been rarer.", "time": "16:56", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 31941, "likes": 149, "replies": 12, "retweets": 28, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Power/grid"]}}, {"id": "2074190205972541836", "url": "https://x.com/gbrew24/status/2074190205972541836", "text": "Factors keeping prices low:\n\n-UAE vs. Saudi price war\n\n-Iran oil building up on the water\n\n-Non-MENA crude flows staying strong (esp. US and Russia)\n\n-No recovery (yet) in Chinese buying. #OOTT", "time": "17:54", "author": "gbrew24", "author_name": "Gregory Brew", "followers": 58007, "views": 30998, "likes": 132, "replies": 6, "retweets": 28, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 36, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["OPEC+", "Supply outlook", "China demand"]}}, {"id": "2074204413347184724", "url": "https://x.com/pickeringenergy/status/2074204413347184724", "text": "My most recent energy commentary (June 30th) - A discussion of oil's downside momentum, our take on why $75/bbl feels more appropriate and the voting machine vs. weighing machine on energy stocks. Your feedback always welcome #EFT #OOTT\n\nhttps://t.co/WjqoEHcOIW", "time": "18:50", "author": "pickeringenergy", "author_name": "Dan Pickering", "followers": 36384, "views": 5224, "likes": 31, "replies": 3, "retweets": 7, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 13, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "finsquawk_", "name": "FinSquawk", "followers": 2496, "tweets": 27, "views": 10521, "likes": 1}, {"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 26, "views": 173421, "likes": 420}, {"username": "DB_WTI", "name": "WTI Trading Group- 🇺🇸 US Crude Oil Trader🛢️🌎", "followers": 12439, "tweets": 14, "views": 11241, "likes": 1}, {"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 8, "views": 680114, "likes": 2405}, {"username": "FluxOfficials", "name": "The Officials", "followers": 1859, "tweets": 7, "views": 4321, "likes": 17}], "top_authors_by_views": [{"username": "JavierBlas", "name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "tweets": 8, "views": 680114, "likes": 2405}, {"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 26, "views": 173421, "likes": 420}, {"username": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "tweet